<br>
There are little tactics you can use which can help such as always making sure you are between the mob and the mezzer before the break and always being ready to move backwards towards the mezzer whilst still hacking away after the mez break just in case. Sometimes if you don't get the agro you can stil manage to obtain it before the mob reaches the fluffy caster. I had a 5 button mouse and I had sit/stand programmed to one of the buttons. Moving backwards whilst clicking sit/stand is usually very effective in getting the mobs attention. Generally, when you lose agro and you are supposed to have it, sitting is often your best hope of regaining it quickly rather than chasing the mob all over the place. The tricks and tactics you will learn on the way to 50 will form how good of a warrior you make in the high end so experiment now when whipes don't really hurt so bad.<br>
<br>
